# Example force-field module for EAM/alloy
# NOTE:
# 1) If your atom types / element order are fixed, you usually only change the EAM file name.
# 2) If you change alloy species or type order, also change the element mapping on pair_coeff line.

pair_style      eam/fs
pair_coeff      * * Ni-Co-Cr_v1.eam.fs Co Cr Ni
